Content Review
==============

Content reviews take a close look at the area from a thematic point of view.
This essentially covers everything cosmetic as well, from the formatting of
the text to the flow of any puzzles and quest-like tasks.

A content reviewer needs to look at the big picture of how the area fits
into DarkWind's overall theme, and more locally to the domain. The area
should be internally consistent thematically, and have a logical form in
terms of room placement, inhabitants, loot etc.

The content reviewer should also look at the quality of any text which is
piped to a player. Ideally, text should both be correct and also have some
stylistic merit.

